          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Source Code</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-gray mb-6">Explore the codebase, contribute, and report issues on GitHub.</p>
          <a href="https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn-core" class="btn btn-outline w-full" target="_blank">View on GitHub</a>
