    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Latest Updates
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-light-slate max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Stay up to date with the latest developments in the ICN ecosystem.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Phase 4 Progress -->
        <div class="card card-hover">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <span class="bg-accent-primary text-midnight-navy text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">DEVELOPMENT</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Phase 4: Federation Devnet</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-gray mb-4">Major progress on federation support, mesh computing infrastructure, and governance systems.</p>
          <a href="/blog/phase-4-progress" class="text-accent-glow hover:underline">Read more ‚Üí</a>
